snippet.title: IGEO DX Open Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
IGEO DX is a challenging Sokoban-like puzzle game available for PC and Mac. It is currently in Open Alpha and playable for free! We're looking for players to break the game and help us find bugs to squash!

Check it out at http://igeogame.com.
